---
// About.astro — Pull quote card + marquee roles, inspired by faisalaffan.com
---

<section id="about" class="section-pad wrap">
  <div class="section-head reveal">
    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow">About</span>
      <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-top:18px">
        Dari kebutuhan<br />menjadi sistem.
      </h2>
    </div>
    <span class="section-index" aria-hidden="true">/ 01 — 07</span>
  </div>

  <div class="about-grid">
    <!-- LEFT: Lead text + pull quote -->
    <div>
      <p class="about-lead reveal">
        Saya menggabungkan <em>rekayasa full-stack</em>, <em>manajemen IT</em> dan <em
          >pemahaman proses bisnis</em
        > untuk membangun sistem yang bukan hanya berjalan — tapi <em>scalable</em>,
        <em>maintainable</em>, dan benar-benar menyelesaikan masalah operasional.
      </p>

      <!-- Pull quote card -->
      <div class="about-pullquote-card reveal" data-d="2">
        <span class="about-pullquote-mark" aria-hidden="true">"</span>
        <p class="about-pullquote-text">
          Build things that last — not just things that look good.
          Technology should serve people, not the other way around.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Role marquee cards -->
      <div class="about-roles-marquee reveal" data-d="3" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="about-roles-track">
          <!-- Set 1 -->
          <div class="role-card">
            <span class="rc-tag">Primary</span>
            <div class="rc-title">IT Manager</div>
            <div class="rc-desc">Memimpin tim & strategi teknis</div>
          </div>
          <div class="role-card">
            <span class="rc-tag">Core</span>
            <div class="rc-title">Full-Stack Dev</div>
            <div class="rc-desc">Laravel, Vue.js, Node.js</div>
          </div>
          <div class="role-card">
            <span class="rc-tag">Specialty</span>
            <div class="rc-title">Solution Architect</div>
            <div class="rc-desc">System design & integration</div>
          </div>
          <div class="role-card">
            <span class="rc-tag">Focus</span>
            <div class="rc-title">ERP Specialist</div>
            <div class="rc-desc">Odoo customization & deployment</div>
          </div>
          <div class="role-card">
            <span class="rc-tag">Growing</span>
            <div class="rc-title">AI Developer</div>
            <div class="rc-desc">AI-assisted business apps</div>
          </div>
          <!-- Set 2 (duplicate for infinite scroll) -->
          <div class="role-card">
            <span class="rc-tag">Primary</span>
            <div class="rc-title">IT Manager</div>
            <div class="rc-desc">Memimpin tim & strategi teknis</div>
          </div>
          <div class="role-card">
            <span class="rc-tag">Core</span>
            <div class="rc-title">Full-Stack Dev</div>
            <div class="rc-desc">Laravel, Vue.js, Node.js</div>
          </div>
          <div class="role-card">
            <span class="rc-tag">Specialty</span>
            <div class="rc-title">Solution Architect</div>
            <div class="rc-desc">System design & integration</div>
          </div>
          <div class="role-card">
            <span class="rc-tag">Focus</span>
            <div class="rc-title">ERP Specialist</div>
            <div class="rc-desc">Odoo customization & deployment</div>
          </div>
          <div class="role-card">
            <span class="rc-tag">Growing</span>
            <div class="rc-title">AI Developer</div>
            <div class="rc-desc">AI-assisted business apps</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- RIGHT: Body text + tags -->
    <div class="about-body reveal" data-d="2">
      <p>
        Dengan pengalaman lebih dari <strong>10 tahun</strong> di industri teknologi, saya
        terbiasa menangani pengembangan sistem end-to-end: mulai dari
        <strong>menggali kebutuhan user, merancang arsitektur aplikasi, membangun
        backend</strong> dan REST API, menata database, hingga menghadirkan antarmuka yang
        rapi dan mudah digunakan.
      </p>
      <p>
        Dalam beberapa tahun terakhir, fokus saya berkembang ke <strong
          >internal business system, workflow automation, ERP/Odoo
          customization, dashboard operasional, dan AI-assisted applications.</strong
        > Saya tertarik membangun teknologi yang praktis — bukan sekadar terlihat modern,
        tetapi benar-benar membantu tim bekerja lebih cepat, lebih terukur, dan lebih efisien.
      </p>

      <div class="about-tags">
        <span class="tag">Laravel &amp; PHP</span>
        <span class="tag">Vue.js</span>
        <span class="tag">REST API</span>
        <span class="tag">Odoo ERP</span>
        <span class="tag">Internal System</span>
        <span class="tag">IT Management</span>
        <span class="tag">AI-Assisted Apps</span>
        <span class="tag">System Design</span>
        <span class="tag">Dashboard &amp; Reporting</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
